Package edu.gmu.cs332.hw5.shapes

Interface Summary
ShapeFactory Provides a common interface through which to access shape factories, following the Abstract Factory design pattern.
 

Class Summary
Geometry Provides common geometric functions for shape geometry.
Line A container class to store attributes about a line segment.
LineTest JUnit tests for the Line class.
Point Point is a cloneable container class representing a point in two-dimensional Cartesian coordinates.
PointTest JUnit tests for the Point class.
Rectangle A container class to store attributes about a rectangle.
RectangleTest JUnit tests for the Rectangle class.
Shape Shape is a generic template interface for various shapes.
Square A container class to store attributes about a square.
SquareTest JUnit tests for the Square class.
